QuestData.Title: Boom Bait
QuestData.Description: There. I've plastered your bird guts over my explosives.$b$bI call 'em Gut Bombs, patent pending.$b$bSince you made friends with these fellas, how about you do the honors?$b$bJust light the fuse and throw 'em down by the shoreline!
QuestData.LogDescription: Use the Gut Bombs at Murky Bank and collect 5 Exploded Slickies.
